OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy with occasional
OL,6,Flight rain but Shetland will become
OL,7,Fmainly dry with sunny spells. Some
OL,8,Fhaar at times over Shetland. Light to
OL,9,Fmoderate southwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry at first over Shetland,
OL,12,Fotherwise it will be cloudy with
OL,13,Fpatchy rain. The rain will turn more
OL,14,Fpersistent and heavier overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FA cloudy start with outbreaks
OL,17,Fof rain, then becoming dry through the
OL,18,Fmorning. Dry with sunny spells in the
OL,19,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
