OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCool
OL,6,Fand breezy with sunshine and passing
OL,7,Fshowers on Tuesday. Dry with long
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells on Wednesday
OL,9,Fand Thursday.
